IDEAS


Begin with a vision for Canada. Governance decisions flow from and must align with the vision


Canada is a profitable country, wealthy, healthy, sovereign and a nation that is attractive to the smartest builders in the world


Vision domains:

- Governance (minimal, transparent)
- Money (sound money standard, zero inflation, decentralized national treasury)
- Justice (law & order, incarceration programs that emphasize rehabilitation and redemption focus)
- Energy (monetize energy resources through bitcoin mining, 
- Health (health incentives funded by sin taxes on unhealthy foods)
- Economic (restoration of free markets, council of anti-complexity)
- Education (monetary literacy, health literacy)
- Immigration (pay to enter, 5 year residency with annual checkin to ensure contribution, deported without refund if law is broken)
- Taxation (flat rate earnings tax, consumption tax, sin tax, immigration tax, foreign corporation tax)


Military protected funds. Council approved spending, transparency focus, energy, health and infrastructure focus

National competitions: development of a health app, development of an SMR that can be produced in volume and purchased by nation, defence drone technology


- The last print: btc treasury, energy infrastructure fund to build nuclear plants across the country, research and produce small modular nuclear reactors
